'''Diyosezi Gatolika ya Byumba''' (Mu Kilatin: ''Dioecesis Byumbanus'') ni agace ka kiliziya cyangwa Diyosezi ya Kiliziya Gatolika ya Roma mu [[Rwanda]] . Yshinzwe ku wa 5 Ugushyingo 1981 na [[:en:Pope_John_Paul_II|Papa Yohani Pawulo wa II]] . Iyi Diyosezi ni imwe mu zigize Akarere k'Ubutumwa ka [[Arikidiyosezi Gatolika ya Kigali|Arikidiyosezi ya Kigali]] .

Servilien Nzakamwita yagizwe Umwepiskopi wa Byumba na Papa Yohani Pawulo wa II ku wa 2 Mutarama 1997.

